143
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,840
It is quite annoying.

144
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:01,600
What about me?

145
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,720
Do I annoy you too?

146
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:08,800
No.

147
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,360
It's getting late.

148
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:25,800
I

149
