150
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,940
I'll walk you back.

151
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:12,860
Jiangling.

152
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,840
I can't sleep,

153
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:16,100
let's go watch the sunrise together.

154
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,880
Then you need to get up early,

155
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,210
go back to sleep for now.

156
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,120
