173
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:28,520
Yes, I can.

174
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,800
What a beautiful sunrise,

175
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:32,660
exactly as I imagined it would be.

176
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,850
I never asked you

177
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:44,520
