182
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:58,890
Actually...

183
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:01,920
I've always struggled to find my direction in life,

184
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:02,580
not knowing

185
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,720
what I could do in the future.

186
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,520
But now,

187
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,640
I think I've found it.

188
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,400
I feel like...

189
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:13,440
Well...

190
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,720
I could become an editor.

191
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,360
Why?

192
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:20,920
Didn't you say

193
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:23,050
you'll become a great writer someday?

194
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:25,250
So I'll be that great writer's editor,

195
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,440
