196
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,600
Keep you on track with your writing.

197
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,600
If you don't submit your work,

198
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,960
I'll come knocking at your door.

199
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,890
How impressive!

200
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,250
Then I better wish you success,

201
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,610
you absolutely must become an editor.

202
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,700
When that happens,

203
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,920
I'll

204
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:43,260
hide somewhere you can't find me.

205
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,600
So you, the great editor,

206
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,600
will be left

207
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:46,800
