208
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:47,640
No way,

209
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,460
I'll definitely find you.

210
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:54,840
But you know,

211
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,320
