212
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,250
you're completely different now.

213
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,580
How am I different?

214
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,720
When I first met you,

215
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,920
