216
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,720
Keeping everyone at a distance.

217
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:11,240
My name is Liu. I'm their English teacher

218
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:13,000
and also their homeroom teacher.

219
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,660
He can start school tomorrow.

220
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:15,920
That's great.

221
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,200
Thank you, Teacher Liu.

222
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,000
This child

223
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,610
doesn't talk much usually.

224
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,760
On the day I transferred,

225
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,800
I was actually feeling really down.

226
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,600
For the college entrance exam,

227
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,260
I transferred to a new school.

228
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:29,940
Everything here felt so unfamiliar.

229
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,080
Only 100 days left

230
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,680
and our high school years

231
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:35,210
will be over just like that.

232
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:36,800
In the end,

233
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,210
what will I have gained?

234
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,840
This name tag that fell at my feet

235
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,240
instantly

236
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:48,800
reminded me of the beginning of many novels.

237
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:49,760
Somehow

238
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:51,620
I felt it was some kind of sign,

239
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:52,800
or

240
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,020
perhaps a mission.

241
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,640
I don't know who gave me this

242
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:56,680
strange feeling.

243
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:57,800
I took it

244
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,680
and made my way to the wishing tree,

245
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:01,010
trying to find answers.

246
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,170
That's when I saw

247
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,640
you appear here too.

248
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:04,920
I didn't know

249
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,640
