250
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,800
I'm afraid I might affect the plot of this novel.

251
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:09,660
Do you know him?

252
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,720
He's handsome.

253
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,160
Is he coming toward me?

254
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:18,840
I think so.

255
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,360
What are you...?

256
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:29,960
Excuse me,

257
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,900
could I get your phone number?

258
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,360
That afternoon,

259
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:34,640
you bought me noodles.

260
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,480
Good evening.

261
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:39,170
Let me treat you to noodles.

262
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,850
You probably don't know

263
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:43,130
