264
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:44,720
In my mind,

265
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,140
except for my aunt,

266
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,140
no one in my life

267
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,560
would bring me food for no reason.

268
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,530
Maybe I've been studying too much,

269
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:54,540
and that's why I overthink things

270
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:56,060
and my brain just crashed.

271
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:57,330
I instinctively

272
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:58,810
