273
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:04,280
Why is this place so crowded too?

274
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:08,820
We need to wait in line.

275
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:14,880
Later I thought

276
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,120
that maybe

277
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,840
you really do love noodles,

278
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:20,080
that we share the same interest,

279
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,400
which I found amazing.

280
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:23,440
I never thought

281
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:25,580
we'd have so many conversations.

282
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:28,440
I usually avoid all contact.

283
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,240
Because...

284
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,560
I've never opened up

285
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:34,360
my inner world to anyone,

286
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:35,800
and I'm afraid to do so.

287
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:36,520
Do you like it?

288
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:36,840
Jiang.

289
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,000
But your presence,

290
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,320
your every move...

291
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:41,000
Yet somehow it made me

292
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,640
lower my defenses without realizing it.

293
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,640
My life

294
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,280
also became happier.

295
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:47,320
That day

296
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:49,960
when you told me about the cross-time calls,

297
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,040
I didn't believe it.

298
00:16:51,040 --> 00:16:52,680
What's with that expression?

