00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:53,680
See for yourself.

300
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:56,680
But I realized

301
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,770
that this matter

302
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,720
deeply affected your emotions.

303
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,320
It led you step by step

304
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:02,840
toward the abyss.

305
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,099
What about him?

306
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:05,619
Did anyone tell you

307
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,800
about the future?

308
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:07,720
I died,

309
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,560
before the college entrance exam.

310
00:17:10,560 --> 00:17:11,960
Making you give yourself

311
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:15,040
increasingly negative psychological suggestions.

312
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,480
I don't want to see you feeling down.

313
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:18,760
I don't know why,

314
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,079
but I want to heal you.

315
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:28,760
Even if this world

316
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,680
truly has predetermined fate,

317
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:32,940
I still want to help you fight against it.

318
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:35,080
I don't want your doomsday

319
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,440
to come true.

320
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,760
If there really is a deity

321
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,200
using this world

322
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,440
to write a novel,

323
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:52,440
and we are its characters,

324
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:54,040
using its invisible hand

325
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:56,160
to lead you step by step into the abyss.

326
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,020
Against death,

327
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,920
I will definitely help you fight it.

328
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:01,240
So,

329
00:18:01,760 --> 00:18:03,200
I wrote a novel too,

330
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:04,760
to be your savior.

331
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,440
To prevent fate

332
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:08,340
from ever taking you away.

333
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,680
I never expected

334
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:12,520
that someone would make copies of my novel

335
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:14,240
and cause you new troubles.

336
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,280
Wait a minute.

337
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,160
She's just called Zhenzhen,

338
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,960
and her 'Zhen' is the 'Zhen' from 'pearl.'

339
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,280
My name is the 'Zhen' that means 'real,'

340
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,280
they're completely different characters.

341
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:23,000
How did you associate that with me?

342
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,060
Do you know why I called you both here?

343
00:18:25,560 --> 00:18:26,160
No idea.

344
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:28,960
I've recently heard some things

345
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,420
about you and An Zhenzhen.

346
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:31,520
I had to call you both

347
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,920
to have a talk about this.

348
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:34,160
They say you're dating too young.

349
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,040
Us dating?

350
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,760
That's completely ridiculous.

351
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,000
To me, you're just

352
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:40,400
like a dim star.

353
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,800
Your energy is getting weaker

354
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,080
and to keep those around you

355
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:47,280
from seeing you fade,

356
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,500
you've been burning yourself up.

357
00:18:50,080 --> 00:18:50,960
While I

358
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,400
am like a glacier.

359
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,930
No matter how much sunlight and fire comes in,

360
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,080
it still can't change my nature.

361
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:01,000
But this time,

362
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:03,640
I actually felt your warmth.

363
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,280
For me,

364
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:08,760
if your light goes out,

365
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:10,480
my world

366
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,130
will return to eternal cold darkness.

367
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:14,760
I can't let that happen.

368
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:16,680
What right do they have to talk about me like that?

369
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:17,680
I paid too,

370
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,930
and my money was stolen as well.

371
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:22,080
I feel wronged too.

372
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,040
No matter what they say,

373
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,320
I believe you.

374
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,000
So,

375
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:48,600
no matter what criticism you face,

376
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:51,440
I will always believe in you.

377
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:54,220
No matter what crisis you encounter,

378
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,880
I will always come

379
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:56,840
to save you.

380
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,160
Now

381
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:08,260
that the dust has settled,

382
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:11,220
you're still standing in front of me.

383
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,480
So Old Jiang's call

384
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,280
was just a nightmare.

385
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:18,000
The story we wrote together

386
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,080
is the real one.

387
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:47,220
Alright

388
00:20:47,320 --> 00:20:49,760
we'll discuss this problem in the next class.

389
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:50,290
By the way

390
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,480
we'll be taking graduation photos the day after tomorrow.

391
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:53,680
The school will organize everyone

392
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,040
to take a group photo.

393
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:57,120
The afternoon self-study sessions for these two days will be canceled.

394
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:58,240
Canceled!

395
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,720
You can find your classmates

396
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:02,320
and teachers to take photos as keepsakes.

397
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:02,960
So

398
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,000
you can use your phones during this time.

399
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:05,560
However

400
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,080
you're not allowed to do anything else

401
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:08,540
just taking photos, okay?

402
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:13,320
I knew it,

403
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,880
as soon as I mentioned using phones,

404
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:18,210
you all got so excited you could barely contain yourselves.

405
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:19,500
Break it up now.

406
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,560
What's up?

407
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,760
Let's go get something to eat.

408
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:30,600
Let's go.

409
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:39,920
Look at you two fighting

410
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,450
and dragging me into it too.

411
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:42,720
You two weren't fighting

412
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:43,360
about me?

413
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:45,440
That was a misunderstanding.

414
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:47,680
The wedding photos weren't good to begin with,

415
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,560
and now there's no chance for divorce photos either.

416
00:21:49,560 --> 00:21:52,290
You're talking as if you two didn't get divorced.

417
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:10,840
What?

418
00:22:12,360 --> 00:22:13,040
As it happens,

419
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:13,960
I just found out

420
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,400
several girls in our class

421
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:17,000
want to take photos with you,

422
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:19,560
so I thought I'd get ahead of them,

423
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:21,760
being in a privileged position and all.

424
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:23,660
You certainly did,

425
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:25,240
there's no one else here.

426
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:27,240
Because I came prepared.

427
00:23:16,440 --> 00:23:17,680
Jiangling.

428
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:20,440
I want to take a photo too!

429
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,040
Hurry up

430
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:22,760
and take our picture!

431
00:23:23,280 --> 00:23:23,940
Take it now!

432
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,530
Let's make a peace sign!

433
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:27,960
Oh no.

434
00:23:33,040 --> 00:23:33,770
An Zhenzhen.

435
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:34,680
What?

436
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:35,500
Gu Ming, get them in position.

437
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:37,240
Hurry up!

438
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:38,960
They're coming, run!

439
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:40,760
Hurry!

440
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:41,840
No, what is this?

441
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:42,400
Guess.

442
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,120
What?

443
00:25:43,360 --> 00:25:44,400
Hurry up.

444
00:25:46,120 --> 00:25:47,040
Stop talking nonsense.

445
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:47,800
Listen to me.

446
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:49,000
I've

447
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,400
planned something special

448
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:52,080
for our class graduation photo.

449
00:25:52,080 --> 00:25:53,280
When the shutter clicks,

450
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:53,800
we'll toss something

451
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:54,760
up in the air,

452
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:56,410
and it'll look amazing.

453
00:25:58,720 --> 00:25:59,480
Save some green for me.

454
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:00,040
Green.

455
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,330
Save some green.

456
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:07,400
What's taking so long?

457
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,400
Hurry up, Qi Shuo.

458
00:26:13,280 --> 00:26:14,240
Did you get my green?

459
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:16,560
Wait for her to press the shutter and throw it.

460
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:17,800
Come on, hurry up.

461
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:18,730
Move in quickly.

462
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:27,840
Stand still.

463
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,130
Did you get my green?

464
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:37,120
That tall person in the back.

465
00:26:37,840 --> 00:26:38,370
Yes, you.

466
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:41,610
Switch places with that girl in front.

467
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:46,720
I mean you.

468
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:52,930
Stand still now.

469
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:54,490
Squat down a bit.

470
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:59,600
Alright, students, time for the photo.

471
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,600
Our two timelines

472
00:28:52,840 --> 00:28:55,040
actually cannot influence each other.

473
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,520
Hawking once said

474
00:28:56,800 --> 00:28:58,800
the universe has an invisible energy

475
00:28:58,800 --> 00:28:59,600
that prevents

476
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:01,960
any attempt to alter its natural course.
